text: Al Asmakh Tower http://wikimapia.org/27780553/Al-Asmakh-Tower/:"Al-Asmakh Tower - Wikimapia" (formerly the IBQ Tower) is a building in West Bay Area in Doha, Qatar. Its design was inspired by New York City landmark Empire State Building. Its height is 227 meters. It has six basements, ground, mezzanine and 34 floors.http://www.constructionweekonline.com/projects-1273-new- headquarters-of-ibq/:"New Headquarters of IBQ Construction Projects ConstructionWeekOnline.com" ==External links== *Al Asmakh Tower ==References== Category:Buildings and structures in Doha
